channel.title: Poject insanity :: item duplication
channel.description:
Many people need help with project insanity, you can dupe on it, you don't even need skill it can be on accident, an accident that is most likley to happen, you mass click an item in trade and it puts more then what you have, and voila... you have easily duped an item.
Also you do offer-x of an item for example, 1 noted phat > offer-x (600) > 600 phats get put in trade when you only had 1, how do you fix it, someone help us?
